{"tid":670074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庫德洛指中國在貿易談判中滿足美國許多要求  但未達成協議","createTime":"2018-05-19T04:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T11:49:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"17545d5d067c2f20dec6f7a0fad344926bce1556","tid":670074,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"庫德洛指中國在貿易談判中滿足美國許多要求  但未達成協議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20180519034039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20180519034039&d=QhqAE%2BowGebsppo1Z3GpxwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0aae31df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20180519034039</a><br />\n<br />\n19/5/2018 3:40<br />\n        白宮經濟顧問庫德洛表示, 中國在貿易談判上滿足美國許多要求, 但仍未達成協議.<br />\n<br />\n       <span style=\"color: red;\"> 他指出, 中國已經提出削減與美國貿易逆差超過2000億美元, 強調中國需要降低關稅, 降低非關稅壁壘, 並接受停止知識產權轉讓的可核查進程.<br />\n</span><br />\n        庫德洛表示, 若與中國的貿易談判沒有成功, 總統特朗普準備獨自採取強硬行, 但認為目前雙方談判進程非常順利."},{"pid":"2fa9e1db80b9894ae38dac60f4bbf093b8f688db","tid":670074,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"無協議即係9up"},{"pid":"7c44f13b964cb6be7127b1bcacf2a8a7ef8d9169","tid":670074,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b22ff2a81f85a73dee927d972d261d11155d853","tid":670074,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:44:23.000Z","msg":"冇聯合聲明=9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013c2543e55f1c60d48d11a4c1e4a86f22d8fc42","tid":670074,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:50:40.000Z","msg":"早一日口交部先否認話冇提2000億⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n睇個款，應該跪哂<br />\n但暫時唔講住，唔想俾人話賣國<br />\nBtw早兩日見人傳共青團微博將哩單野比喻為辛亥條約<br />\n應該一出協議，對內就玩民族主義屌美國<br />\n黎掩飾支共既無能"},{"pid":"8412b5d83fa7e066d6c9a4a75f86f93f94208015","tid":670074,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:59:57.000Z","msg":"跪係度含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6b8bf85e280d5b28eeb147f2cc7f91e04f826d","tid":670074,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1dce2ab81b0e7337e66601988a8f722a719892c0","tid":670074,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:27:14.000Z","msg":"美帝：屎總含得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我唔夠舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4533b5a7d8d3e3131b1cbb4f74907bec2320460c","tid":670074,"uid":104699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:30:36.000Z","msg":"唔到佢唔含啦，不過含又死唔含又死。南美都爆緊，阿根廷同巴西匯率大貶緊，支那嘅出口市場開始萎縮，簽埋減2000億逆差支那真係食粥水"},{"pid":"bd83c7d95744809244ca7525522843534f52c85c","tid":670074,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:57:05.000Z","msg":"重點要逐年檢查 贏國有冇遵守"},{"pid":"1f640155bdd8be7ca6136c5790bc2ef4e4911321","tid":670074,"uid":32722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd83c7d95744809244ca7525522843534f52c85c","tid":670074,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:57:05.000Z","msg":"重點要逐年檢查 贏國有冇遵守"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"係逐季"},{"pid":"5c927affd57abc0a0f8560817628d4bdf9afff32","tid":670074,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"美國佬叫你嘔逆差<br />\n嘔少一蚊都唔得掂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔夠膽、冇本事開美國佬拖係咁<i